pr_body:
**Description**

This PR will, give us an overall compatibility of different adapters.

This PR fixes #2515 

**Notes for Reviewers**
Works left:
1. Filter overall compatibility according to Meshery Server version
2. Calculate the overall server version and assign suitable color code to it

Question:
If we are displaying the adapter compatibility according to the Meshery Server version, there will be adapters for which we don't haven test for a particular version, so what should we do in that case? 

My idea:
We display all the adapter in all cases and if the adapter does not have any test on a particular Meshery Server version, we show a gray color on the overall compatibility field with text : No test run for this server version.
